    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
        <body>
            <div xml:id="KT391-kilavi">
                <p type="edition">piriviṭaip paruvavaraviṉkaṇ āṟṟāḷ eṉak kavaṉṟa tōḻikkuk kiḻatti
                    aḻintu colliyatu. </p>


                <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Uttered when being desolate by HER to the
                    confidante, who was anxious she would not have the strength at the coming of the
                    season in the time of separation. </p>
            </div>

            <div xml:id="KT391">
                <lg type="edition">
                    <l> uvari yorutta luḻātu maṭiyap</l>
                    <l> pukari puḻuṅkiya puyaṉīṅku puṟaviṟ</l>
                    <l> kaṭitiṭi yurumiṟ pāmpupai yaviya</l>
                    <l> vitiyoṭu mayaṅki yiṉituvīḻn taṉṟē</l>
                    <l> vīḻnta māmaḻai taḻīip pirintōr</l>
                    <l> kaiyaṟa vanta paiyuṇ mālaip</l>
                    <l> pūñciṉai yirunta pōḻkaṇ maññai</l>
                    <l> tānīr naṉantalai pulampak</l>
                    <l> kūun tōḻi perumpē taiyavē.</l>


                </lg>

                <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <l rend="indent"> On the woodlands left by clouds which was sultry for the deer,</l>
                    <l rend="indent2"> while the bull droops without ploughing in the brackish
                        water,</l>
                    <l> sweets have descended, mixed with thunder,</l>
                    <l rend="indent3"> for the snake hood to shrink in heavily thundering thunder.</l>
                    <l> [These] very foolish [birds] are cooing, friend,</l>
                    <l rend="indent2"> while the vast area becomes lonely in the rushing water,</l>
                    <l rend="indent"> the peacocks with wide open [tails'] eyes,</l>
                    <l rend="indent9"> perched on flowering branches,</l>
                    <l rend="indent3"> in sorrowful evening, so that action subsides</l>
                    <l rend="indent4"> in those who are separated,</l>
                    <l rend="indent6"> when the great rain that fell envelopes [them].</l>


                </lg>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
